English | 5 hours | AVC 960x720 25 fps | AAC 64 Kbps 44.1 KHz | 506 MB
Genre: Video Training


A Practical Ruby Training Course That Teaches Real World Skills
In this project-based Ruby Programming video tutorial series, you'll quickly have relevant skills for real-world applications.

Follow along with our expert instructor in this training course to get:

Concise, informative and broadcast-quality Ruby Programming training videos delivered to your desktop
The ability to learn at your own pace with our intuitive, easy-to-use interface
A quick grasp of even the most complex Ruby Programming subjects because they're broken into simple, easy to follow tutorial videos

Practical working files further enhance the learning process and provide a degree of retention that is unmatched by any other form of Ruby Programming tutorial, online or offline... so you'll know the exact steps for your own projects.
